## Phase 7: Production & Deployment ðŸš€

### 7.1 Performance Optimization
**Goal**: Scale to hundreds of concurrent students

**Features**:
- Database optimization and caching
- CDN integration for assets
- API response time optimization
- Client-side performance improvements

**Implementation**:
- Optimize database queries and indexing
- Implement Redis caching layer
- Add CDN for static assets
- Profile and optimize client-side code

**Estimated Effort**: 3-4 weeks

### 7.2 Security & Privacy
**Goal**: FERPA compliance and student data protection

**Features**:
- Student data encryption and privacy
- FERPA compliance implementation
- Secure authentication systems
- Audit logging and compliance reporting

**Implementation**:
- Implement end-to-end encryption
- Add compliance frameworks
- Build secure authentication
- Create audit and logging systems

**Estimated Effort**: 4-6 weeks

### 7.3 Deployment Infrastructure
**Goal**: Production-ready hosting and monitoring

**Features**:
- Cloud deployment automation
- Monitoring and alerting systems
- Backup and disaster recovery
- Scalable infrastructure management

**Implementation**:
- Set up cloud infrastructure (AWS/Azure/GCP)
- Implement monitoring with Datadog/New Relic
- Create backup and recovery procedures
- Build auto-scaling systems

**Estimated Effort**: 3-5 weeks

